[
    {
        "text": "Plato once said, \"Seek truth while you are young,...\"",
        "startTime": 1834,
        "endTime": 4344,
        "slowStartTime": 2901,
        "slowEndTime": 6741
    },
    {
        "text": "\"...for if you do not, it will later escape your grasp.\"",
        "startTime": 4553,
        "endTime": 7121,
        "slowStartTime": 6980,
        "slowEndTime": 10906
    },
    {
        "text": "Recently, a conference in Rome studied the broader implications of Plato's quote.",
        "startTime": 7590,
        "endTime": 11636,
        "slowStartTime": 11535,
        "slowEndTime": 17679
    },
    {
        "text": "The conference was called \"Philosophy as Paideia,\"...",
        "startTime": 12169,
        "endTime": 14623,
        "slowStartTime": 18404,
        "slowEndTime": 22159
    },
    {
        "text": "...a reference to the well-rounded education of ancient times.",
        "startTime": 14975,
        "endTime": 17836,
        "slowStartTime": 22612,
        "slowEndTime": 26979
    },
    {
        "text": "Participants discussed how to think...",
        "startTime": 18104,
        "endTime": 19818,
        "slowStartTime": 27306,
        "slowEndTime": 29952
    },
    {
        "text": "...but also how to teach the discipline in a more practical way.",
        "startTime": 20007,
        "endTime": 22915,
        "slowStartTime": 30160,
        "slowEndTime": 34598
    },
    {
        "text": "For example, for a doctor, philosophy is useful for reflecting on what makes someone human...",
        "startTime": 23665,
        "endTime": 28361,
        "slowStartTime": 35647,
        "slowEndTime": 42766
    },
    {
        "text": "...or what suffering means.",
        "startTime": 28435,
        "endTime": 29865,
        "slowStartTime": 42803,
        "slowEndTime": 45022
    },
    {
        "text": "Philosophy can even help an engineer.",
        "startTime": 30138,
        "endTime": 32159,
        "slowStartTime": 45357,
        "slowEndTime": 48464
    },
    {
        "text": "An engineer can use a different mindset to think about a technique or what it means.",
        "startTime": 32497,
        "endTime": 37112,
        "slowStartTime": 48895,
        "slowEndTime": 55893
    },
    {
        "text": "The professors believe that philosophy helps develop self-esteem and personality.",
        "startTime": 37560,
        "endTime": 41663,
        "slowStartTime": 56490,
        "slowEndTime": 62719
    },
    {
        "text": "They say it is crucial for a young person's formation.",
        "startTime": 41916,
        "endTime": 44255,
        "slowStartTime": 63024,
        "slowEndTime": 66608
    },
    {
        "text": "We see that there is a very present demand for philosophy,...",
        "startTime": 44373,
        "endTime": 47709,
        "slowStartTime": 66709,
        "slowEndTime": 71788
    },
    {
        "text": "...which is basically a desire to know.",
        "startTime": 47815,
        "endTime": 49985,
        "slowStartTime": 71873,
        "slowEndTime": 75202
    },
    {
        "text": "And you don't expect it but people need this.",
        "startTime": 50241,
        "endTime": 52655,
        "slowStartTime": 75511,
        "slowEndTime": 79208
    },
    {
        "text": "The Pontifical University of the Holy Cross organized the conference.",
        "startTime": 53135,
        "endTime": 56766,
        "slowStartTime": 79853,
        "slowEndTime": 85374
    },
    {
        "text": "It drew an international group of businesspeople, teachers and philosophers.",
        "startTime": 56854,
        "endTime": 61042,
        "slowStartTime": 85431,
        "slowEndTime": 91788
    }
]